title: Writing, Part 2—Essay
intro_text:
Writing, Part 2—Essay

Welcome to the Writing, Part 2—Essay Practice Test.

You have 45 minutes to complete the test. Read the passages and prompt carefully and write a complete response to the prompt. The goal is to give you practice on the type of essay question you will see on the HiSET® test and to help us understand what you need to brush up on for the test.

Relax and do your best!
